aa(lp400
VAnd that brings us
p401
aVto skill number three,
p402
aVthe ability to implement this,
p403
aVto get colleagues across the entire chain
p404
aVto actually do these things.
p405
aVAnd it's been slow to spread.
p406
aVThis is not yet our norm in surgery \u2014
p407
aVlet alone making checklists
p408
aVto go onto childbirth and other areas.
p409
aVThere's a deep resistance
p410
aVbecause using these tools
p411
aVforces us to confront
p412
aVthat we're not a system,
p413
aVforces us to behave with a different set of values.
p414
aVJust using a checklist
p415
aVrequires you to embrace different values from the ones we've had,
p416
aVlike humility,
p417
aVdiscipline,
p418
aVteamwork.
p419
aVThis is the opposite of what we were built on:
p420
aVindependence, self-sufficiency,
p421
aVautonomy.
