aa(lp423
VI met an actual cowboy, by the way.
p424
aVI asked him, what was it like
p425
aVto actually herd a thousand cattle
p426
aVacross hundreds of miles?
p427
aVHow did you do that?
p428
aVAnd he said, "We have the cowboys stationed at distinct places all around."
