aa(lp439
VMaking systems work
p440
aVis the great task of my generation
p441
aVof physicians and scientists.
p442
aVBut I would go further and say
p443
aVthat making systems work,
p444
aVwhether in health care, education,
p445
aVclimate change,
p446
aVmaking a pathway out of poverty,
p447
